import React from 'react'; import { Card } from 'react-bootstrap'; import SVG from "react-inlinesvg"; import { toAbsoluteUrl } from "../../../../../../_metronic/_helpers"; import { CardBody } from '../../../../../../_metronic/_partials/controls'; import { format, parseISO } from 'date-fns'; export function RejectToRejectView(props) { const paymentVerification = props.paymentVerification; const paymentInfo = props.paymentInfo; const salesOfficerLocation = props.salesOfficerLocation; return ( <>
{format(parseISO(paymentInfo.actionTakenDate), 'HH:mm a')}
{format(parseISO(paymentInfo.actionTakenDate), 'dd MMM yyyy')}
{paymentInfo.actionTakenBy.name}
{paymentInfo.collectionBy.designation.name}
Payment Verification {paymentVerification == "REJECTED" ? "Rejected" : ""}

{paymentInfo.rejectReason}

{format(parseISO(paymentInfo.paymentDate), 'HH:mm a')}
{format(parseISO(paymentInfo.paymentDate), 'dd MMM yyyy')}
{paymentInfo.collectionBy.name}
{paymentInfo.collectionBy.designation.name}, {salesOfficerLocation.location_type} ({salesOfficerLocation.location_name})
Payment Collection

{paymentInfo.remarks}

); }
